the supporting groups , theoretical work is done to develop methods and principles for the construction and efficient use of distributed and parallel computer systems . typo3search_end end # main-content2col-home latest system news posted on 22 march 2013 in system news : new cluster arrived : " oculus " click here to learn more about oculus . latest news posted on 13 june 2014 in talks : analyzing interrupt latencies and data transmission timings for qnx and rt linux using intecrio date : 16 june 2014 , 16 : 00 in o2.267 hermanth jormarnahalli venkatappa posted on 07 march 2014 in talks : implementation of embedding and monitoring modules for a resource orchestrating network virtualization platform date : 11 march 2014 , 15 : 00 in o2.267 aditya neelkanth posted on 04 december 2013 in talks : services des pc2 : status und zuk ü nftige entwicklung date : 19 december 2013 , 16 : 00 in o2.267 ( geb ä ude o ) das pc ² m ö chte sie ü ber den stand seiner infrastruktur und die anstehenden ä nderungen informieren. folgende themen sind u.a. geplant : 1. oculus - dieses system ist nun seit 8 monaten in betrieb und.. . end # right-content-home copyright © 2008-2011 paderborn center for parallel computing · imprint · sitemap end # container
